products.title: Lifetime Grain Brilliant White
products.description: Lifetime grain brilliantwhite will bring a fresh, modern feel to any room. Reflecting all the light into the room when open, this will give the perfect finish to the contemporary room you've created. Their outstanding quality lifetime blinds are made to the same high standards as all their other venetian blinds - we are confident you will not buy better quality blinds, backed by their 3 year guarantee.
